summary:
Adds a playable viking race with new power called cold bones
The vikings male have darker voice and are a little longer
The vikings female are little longer
This mod adds the viking race and a new viking horse(Icelandic horse)the horse can be found to the left of the sign next to whiterunstables shown in pic I KNOW that vikings was normal length
descriptionHtml:
Adds a playable viking race with new power called cold bones
The vikings male have darker voice and are a little longer
The vikings female are little longer
This mod adds the viking race and a new viking horse(Icelandic horse)the horse can be found to the left of the sign next to whiterunstables shown in pic I KNOW that vikings was normal length and and things like that but this is a mod
The race bonuses is (onehanded 10 block 10 archery 5 smithing 5 heavyarmor 5 lightarmor 5 speech 5)
